channel.description:
Hey Guys, Thought Id Post My Current Project Here So You Guys Could Check It.
Features: Mining Smithing Smelting Fletching (With Interfaces) Cooking (Better then Rs Lol) Fishing Runecrafting Slayer (Slayer Tasks Ftw) Working Prayer, With Effects, Icons, And Switching. 100% Range, Arrow Draw Back, Arrow Usage, Projectiles, Everything Herblore. Theiving Crafting, And Woodcutting. Own Client New RS Style / Gameframe. Music Effects / Game Effects. Monsters Dont No-Clip When Attacked, So You Can Hide Behind Things And Range Etc. 100% Working God Wars Mini-Game. Skill Cape Emotes 100% Trading, No Trade Glitchs, Dupes Etc. Working Friends List. Shows Online / Offline Users. Added Taverly Doungen / Jonny Style! Many New Skill Areas 1 v 1 In Edgeville. Runes For Magic No Lag Perfect Gfx Perfect DDS Special. Multiple Pk Zones
